game.name: Thumb vs thumb
game.description:
This time a new type of arcade puzzle challenge has hit your gaming screen! Yes, you have to be a part of the first and highly exciting fighting challenge where two thumbs will get participated in the Old West. One out of the two thumbs will be yours. Many armed inches have just invaded the Saloon. You are the person who has the ability to sort out this conflict. Put your quick reflexes and brain abilities to calm them down by just unsheathing the first!

The fighting challenging might be bigger than you thought of since both thumbs are ready to face each other with full of aggression. When you click the play button, you would see a button placing between them. Keep pressing the button to score points and you can track your score on the right lower side of the screen in this cool puzzle game! Make sure that your opponent would not block your thumb otherwise you would lose the game. 

The player who will reach the score of 500 first will win the game. Do you think that you are strong enough to taste the victory in each effort? Play this excellent fun HTML5 2-players game challenge to keep you busy for hours! The best part is that you do not have to download any app to enjoy this in your gaming device. Enjoy it alone or invite your friends to spot some precious funny and entertaining hours!
